{"tid":539171,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人試過耳屎多到入肉","createTime":"2018-01-24T10:28:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-27T04:20:46.000Z","uid":120202,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"f9f26ffd3b723ec4f06bc3abb64a449c25907a0f","tid":539171,"uid":120202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T10:28:19.000Z","msg":"求先睇專科 佢用鏡照到左耳比耳屎塞曬 <br />\n醫生話d耳屎蝕到入肉 要夾硬夾出黎<br />\n成個過程痛撚到升天 痛過生仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  因為d耳屎癡住皮膚同肉 要夾咁大舊出黎就會扯損d部位 而且耳仔連接好多神經 佢一扯個種痛係大腦痛全身痛痛到暈咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n經歷左差唔多一個鐘終於清完 痛到瀨屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  醫生話兩邊耳仔都因為耳屎太多搞到耳道變形 失去自己排耳屎既能力 可能呢一世都要定期搵佢清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n奉勸大家真係要保護好耳仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5da7dd3aba1198e0e3a051a04c87a2889ed2aea","tid":539171,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T10:30:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"99683dafca6c2e599e0173bbd146b0af7e4de894","tid":539171,"uid":120202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5da7dd3aba1198e0e3a051a04c87a2889ed2aea","tid":539171,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T10:30:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T10:32:02.000Z","msg":"佢都有幫我吸 但大部分都因為太硬同癡實d肉所以要用鉗慢慢挖鬆再夾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\